
Overview of noun totalitarian

The noun totalitarian has 1 sense (no senses from tagged texts)
                                  
1. totalitarian -- (an adherent of totalitarian principles or totalitarian government)

Overview of adj totalitarian

The adj totalitarian has 2 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                    
1. (1) totalitarian -- (characterized by a government in which the political authority exercises absolute and centralized control; "a totalitarian regime crushes all autonomous institutions in its drive to seize the human soul"- Arthur M.Schlesinger, Jr.)
2. totalitarian, totalistic -- (of or relating to the principles of totalitarianism according to which the state regulates every realm of life; "totalitarian theory and practice"; "operating in a totalistic fashion")
